<h1>Sony WH-1000XM5 Review (2026): Still the Noise-Canceling King?</h1>
<div class="meta">
<span><time datetime="2026-05-02">May 2, 2026</time></span>
<span>鈴憋笍 11 min read</span>
<span class="badge">Headphones</span>
